### 2. Bank Account Enhancements

**File:** [add_account_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/aslucky18/finanalyzer/lib/features/accounts/ui/add_account_screen.dart)

- **Account types** restricted to: `Savings`, `Salary`, [Current](file:///c:/Users/aslucky18/finanalyzer/lib/features/auth/services/auth_service.dart#38-50), `Credit card`
- **Last 4 digits** enforced to exactly 4 numeric digits using `FilteringTextInputFormatter` + `LengthLimitingTextInputFormatter`
