### 5. Settings вЂ“ Delete Account

**File:** [settings_screen.dart](file:///c:/Users/aslucky18/finanalyzer/lib/features/auth/ui/settings_screen.dart)

- New **"Delete Account"** `ListTile` below "Sign Out" (red text, trash icon)
- Shows a confirmation dialog: *"This will permanently delete your account and all associated data. This action cannot be undone."*
- On confirm: calls `authService.deleteUserAccount()` в†’ deletes profile row в†’ calls Supabase admin delete в†’ redirects to Login screen

**AuthService** now has [deleteUserAccount()](file:///c:/Users/aslucky18/finanalyzer/lib/features/auth/services/auth_service.dart):
```dart
Future<void> deleteUserAccount() async {
  await _supabase.from('user_profiles').delete().eq('id', user.id);
  await _supabase.auth.admin.deleteUser(user.id);
}
```

