> [!NOTE]
> The [deleteUserAccount](file:///c:/Users/aslucky18/finanalyzer/lib/features/auth/services/auth_service.dart#117-127) method calls `_supabase.auth.admin.deleteUser()`. This requires your Supabase project to have the service role key set up on your backend, or you may want to use a Supabase Edge Function that performs this with the service role. Alternatively, call [signOut](file:///c:/Users/aslucky18/finanalyzer/lib/features/auth/services/auth_service.dart#33-36) and a Supabase database trigger/cascade can delete all user data.
